Add this CSS inside the existing <style> block after the .app rule:

.test-banner {
  margin-bottom: 18px;
  border: 1px solid #facc15;
  border-radius: 8px;
  background: #422006;
  color: #fef3c7;
  padding: 12px 14px;
  font-weight: 700;
}

Add this HTML immediately inside <div class="app"> before <div class="header">:

<div class="test-banner" role="status">Test banner active</div>
